<collectingRegion box="[548,684,1539,1566]" country="Canada" name="Nova Scotia" pageId="3" pageNumber="360">Nova Scotia</collectingRegion>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Peck and Stephan" box="[726,993,1539,1566]" firstAuthor="Peck" pageId="3" pageNumber="360" pagination="667 - 741" refId="ref23890" refString="Peck SB, Stephan K (1996) A revision of the genus Colon Herbst (Coleoptera: Leiodidae: Coloninae) of North America. The Canadian Entomologist 128: 667 - 741." type="journal article" year="1996">Peck and Stephan 1996</bibRefCitation>
